content.name: Relocated Clusters
content.author: Chem O`Dun
content.description:
Transform the entire Galaxy with a single click!
This extension allows you to relocate existing clusters to a new position on the Galaxy Map.
Important notice!
This feature requires the external utility Cluster Relocation Service to function.
Please re-download version 1.2.0 from the https://www.nexusmods.com/x4foundations/mods/1835/.
